31:09.135 --> 31:12.504
SWITCH:
What happened?

31:12.538 --> 31:14.540
DAVID:
They gave me away.

31:14.573 --> 31:17.910
Why did she give me away?

31:21.280 --> 31:23.282
What was wrong with me?

31:25.084 --> 31:26.552
Why didn't you love me?

31:26.585 --> 31:30.022
(baby gurgles)

31:30.056 --> 31:34.226
What if I pass it on to him?

31:34.260 --> 31:37.463
And he ends up like me?

31:39.398 --> 31:41.567
Would you rather he be like me?

31:41.600 --> 31:44.270
-Yes.
-(laughs)

31:44.303 --> 31:46.305
I wouldn't.

31:47.739 --> 31:50.142
No. He'll be fine.

31:52.444 --> 31:53.845
He'll be himself.

31:56.615 --> 31:58.617
(cooing)

