Hey, you.

32:28.347 --> 32:30.349
Little baby me.

32:31.850 --> 32:35.854
So small. So happy.

32:35.887 --> 32:38.524
Is your mommy being good?

32:38.557 --> 32:41.660
Do you feel loved?

32:43.495 --> 32:45.864
Something scary is coming.

32:45.897 --> 32:49.168
Don't worry, I'm here.

32:49.201 --> 32:51.770
I'll protect you.

32:51.803 --> 32:53.805
(muffled music playing)

33:04.983 --> 33:08.454
Charles, my love.

33:08.487 --> 33:10.956
I think this house is haunted.

