I hear voices.
There's a presence.

33:14.560 --> 33:17.396
Or maybe it's the sickness
coming back.

33:17.429 --> 33:19.731
Maybe I'm the one
who's haunted.

33:19.765 --> 33:23.535
When I sleep, I feel something

33:23.569 --> 33:26.738
beautiful watching over me.

33:26.772 --> 33:29.408
But when I'm awake,

33:29.441 --> 33:33.212
the shadow seems to move.

33:33.245 --> 33:35.847
Charles, my love.

33:35.881 --> 33:37.849
Why did you leave me all alone?

33:37.883 --> 33:39.885
(muffled music continues)

