Damn it.

34:33.605 --> 34:34.573
(fussing)

34:34.606 --> 34:36.875
(crying)

34:36.908 --> 34:41.213
No, no, no, no. Not the TV.

34:41.247 --> 34:43.315
Don't you see?

34:43.349 --> 34:46.785
No, look out.
He's behind you.

34:46.818 --> 34:49.588
David, cry.

